text: François d'Harcourt (10 December 1928 – 5 November 2020) was a French politician. He was born in Paris. d'Harcourt was a member of the Union for French Democracy. He was a member of the National Assembly from 1973 to 1997. d'Harcourt died on 5 November 2020 in Annecy, France at the age of 91. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Politicians from Paris
title: François d'Harcourt
